00:36:54,240 --> 00:36:55,240
Stir up some buzz.

865
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:56,720
To be honest,

866
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,160
I've been thinking about this very thing.

867
00:36:59,160 --> 00:37:00,000
That's wonderful!

868
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:00,960
What have you been thinking?

869
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:01,880
Tell us about it.

870
00:37:02,160 --> 00:37:04,680
We need to dig deep into the historical roots,

871
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:06,280
empower it with culture.

872
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:08,960
The origin of Taohua Town's dragon boat race

873
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:10,400
is different from other places.

874
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:11,240
The Jing County Annals,

875
00:37:11,680 --> 00:37:13,080
in the 18th year of Qianlong, records

876
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,120
four characters:

877
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:16,160
"Mountains collapsed and rivers ran dry."

878
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:17,640
These four characters,

879
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,040
what do they tell us?

880
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:20,320
In ancient times,

881
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:21,520
our Jing County

882
00:37:22,160 --> 00:37:25,360
frequently had landslides and mudslides.

883
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:27,640
Customers from north and south

884
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:29,200
couldn't get into Taohua Town,

885
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:31,400
and the paper couldn't be sold.

886
00:37:32,480 --> 00:37:34,520
So our Taohua Town

887
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:36,680
organized its own fleet of boats,

888
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:40,680
down the Qingyi River into the Yangtze,

889
00:37:41,080 --> 00:37:45,000
delivering paper to Nanjing and Shanghai.

890
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:47,040
It solved the local livelihood problem.

891
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:50,000
Later, this waterway fell out of use,

892
00:37:50,640 --> 00:37:52,120
and the local folks

893
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:54,960
began holding dragon boat races

894
00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:57,120
to commemorate those days.

895
00:37:58,560 --> 00:37:59,440
Seriously?

896
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,600
What evidence do you have to refute me?

897
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:02,800
Well...

898
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,240
You've got nothing, right?

899
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:05,640
I do.

900
00:38:05,640 --> 00:38:06,440
Let's hear it.

901
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:09,480
Linjia Village has made Xuan paper since ancient times.

902
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:12,640
Later, the Xuan paper industry grew,

903
00:38:12,640 --> 00:38:13,680
and labor was further divided

904
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:15,920
to process wingceltis bark and rice straw.

905
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,040
The key point is,

906
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:19,560
it's still tied to our Xuan paper.

907
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:22,400
Still trying to tie it to Xuan paper, huh?

908
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:23,880
Old Liao,

909
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:26,560
look, you're now a big-name blogger

910
00:38:26,560 --> 00:38:28,840
with hundreds of thousands of followers.

911
00:38:29,040 --> 00:38:31,600
You're Taohua Town's tourism spokesperson.

912
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:34,520
Every word and action of yours must be careful.

913
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:35,320
Mind the impact.

914
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:37,960
Anything unfounded can't be said.

915
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,920
Which of my words is unfounded?

916
00:38:40,120 --> 00:38:40,920
I'm not afraid to debate.

917
00:38:41,040 --> 00:38:43,120
The more you debate, the clearer the truth.

918
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:44,720
If you were on solid ground,

919
00:38:44,720 --> 00:38:46,960
you wouldn't have been nicknamed "Triple Fail."

920
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:49,360
There are so many mouths online,

921
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:50,520
