924
00:38:53,160 --> 00:38:54,680
I'm just reminding you of one thing.

925
00:38:55,040 --> 00:38:57,560
You now represent us officially.

926
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:58,880
So,

927
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,560
every historical story you tell

928
00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:02,040
must have basis in official history.

929
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,360
Basis in official history?

930
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:04,000
Yes.

931
00:39:05,560 --> 00:39:07,280
Then I can't do this promotion.

932
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,000
Look at you.

933
00:39:08,520 --> 00:39:09,040
What?

934
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:10,600
Gone big-shot influencer and let it get to your head?

935
00:39:10,600 --> 00:39:11,920
Butting heads even with the Secretary?

936
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,160
Secretary Peng,

937
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:18,040
I apologize for my attitude.

938
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:19,400
However,

939
00:39:20,120 --> 00:39:21,440
on academic matters,

940
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:23,120
I stand by my views.

941
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:24,120
Academic, my foot.

942
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:24,680
You...

943
00:39:24,680 --> 00:39:25,400
Here's the deal.

944
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:28,320
The last Four Treasures of the Study

945
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,960
Festival was overseen by Lin Yiran herself.

946
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,200
Discuss it with her.

947
00:39:31,200 --> 00:39:32,120
Keep in mind,

948
00:39:32,600 --> 00:39:34,920
don't overplay it in promotion.

949
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:37,920
Big facts true, small details flexible.

950
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:38,640
Alright.

951
00:39:39,560 --> 00:39:40,480
Rest assured,

952
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:42,120
I'll present it in a way

953
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:44,920
that's airtight and reasonable.

954
00:40:05,600 --> 00:40:06,120
Sis

955
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:08,080
Here, try what I fried

956
00:40:08,080 --> 00:40:08,640
Okay

957
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:10,840
Careful, it's hot

958
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,840
Crispy outside, tender inside

959
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,400
So delicious

960
00:40:19,120 --> 00:40:20,400
Your Maolin Twelve Dishes,

961
00:40:20,520 --> 00:40:21,960
you're about to surpass me

962
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:23,720
I wouldn't dare

963
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,720
The key is I have a great teacher

964
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,280
Not only do you teach well,

965
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:29,040
