966
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:31,440
Just look at young Lin

967
00:40:31,680 --> 00:40:34,400
Fit for the parlor and the kitchen.

968
00:40:34,640 --> 00:40:35,800
I really adore her

969
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:38,320
Her cooking skills

970
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:39,600
