973
00:40:43,560 --> 00:40:44,280
That's right

974
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:46,880
Ran the restaurant just to get by

975
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:48,080
Back then,

976
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,880
no one had time to watch Yiran

977
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:51,800
So she stayed with grandma and helped cook

978
00:40:51,880 --> 00:40:53,880
Around third grade, I think

979
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:56,520
No wonder my son

980
00:40:56,640 --> 00:40:58,880
