981
00:40:59,120 --> 00:40:59,600
Really?

982
00:41:00,200 --> 00:41:00,720
Well,

983
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:02,680
back when I had the restaurant,

984
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:03,720
