985
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:05,520
Yiran was always the first to try it

986
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,840
How could she not learn?

987
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:08,040
See?

988
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,600
That's why I can tell young Lin

989
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:12,160
