990
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:16,000
As the old saying goes,

991
00:41:16,720 --> 00:41:20,000
You raised me, I'll care for you when old.

992
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,640
Kids grow up

993
00:41:22,640 --> 00:41:25,320
You don't see her infuriating side, sis

994
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:26,920
I don't care about that

995
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,360
I've got to learn from you

996
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,720
I want young Lin

997
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:31,600
