1001
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,520
I need to discuss with you

1002
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:40,960
What is it? Go ahead

1003
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:42,000
Do we need to discuss it?

1004
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:42,760
It's like this

1005
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:45,680
I have some old insurance clients

1006
00:41:45,680 --> 00:41:47,400
