1016
00:42:03,080 --> 00:42:04,440
They can use it too

1017
00:42:04,640 --> 00:42:06,040
I'll be your salesperson

1018
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:07,040
What do you think?

1019
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,600
Sis

1020
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:11,920
Between our two families,

1021
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:14,600
