1022
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:15,800
We Xuans

1023
00:42:15,800 --> 00:42:16,640
may not have much else,

1024
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:18,080
but paper? All you need

1025
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:19,360
Really?

1026
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:20,440
Really

1027
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:22,040
But,

1028
00:42:22,520 --> 00:42:23,720
you just got out of the hospital

1029
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:25,880
Running around like this,

1030
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:27,520
