1031
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:29,360
She can't tell me what to do

1032
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:31,640
Isn't this great for both our families?

1033
00:42:31,640 --> 00:42:32,160
Right?

1034
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:32,640
Yes, yes, yes

1035
00:42:32,640 --> 00:42:34,000
Then it's settled

1036
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:34,920
Honestly,

1037
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:36,000
if you asked me to come up with

1038
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,360
that much cash all at once

1039
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,120
to buy the paper,

1040
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,680
I definitely couldn't afford it

1041
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:40,800
Here's what we'll do

1042
00:42:41,240 --> 00:42:42,160
Tomorrow

1043
00:42:42,360 --> 00:42:43,880
I'll find a big truck

1044
00:42:44,480 --> 00:42:46,040
