1045
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:47,800
Take it to the senior university first

1046
00:42:48,640 --> 00:42:49,440
Then it's settled

1047
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:51,800
Come, come

1048
00:42:51,800 --> 00:42:52,680
Settled, settled

1049
00:42:52,680 --> 00:42:53,040
Settled

1050
00:42:53,040 --> 00:42:53,640
Quick, quick

1051
00:42:53,640 --> 00:42:55,440
I'll call them right away

1052
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:57,560
Good, good, come on
